OL,3,C'Hardest video I've ever had to make':
OL,4,CKSI announces sudden Sidemen departure
OL,6,FSocial media star and Britain's Got
OL,7,FTalent judge KSI has announced he is
OL,8,Fleaving the YouTube collective Sidemen.
OL,10,FThe 32-year-old, whose real name is
OL,11,FOlajide Olatunji, has made football,
OL,12,Fcomedy and challenge videos with the
OL,13,Fgroup since 2013.
OL,15,FIn a post on YouTube, KSI said: "This
OL,16,Fis honestly the hardest video I've
OL,17,Fever had to make in my life.
OL,26,@wD@aOU
