OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780326668
OL,3,C'Hardest video I've ever had to make':
OL,4,CKSI announces sudden Sidemen departure
OL,6,F"I've gone back and forth on this
OL,7,Fdecision for a very long time. I've
OL,8,Fspent months trying to figure out what
OL,9,Fthe right thing to do is.
OL,11,F"But after a lot of thought, I've
OL,12,Fdecided that I will no longer be doing
OL,13,Fsidemen videos. Today, 31st of May,
OL,14,Fwill be my final Sidemen video.
OL,16,F"Even saying those words out loud
OL,17,Fdoesn't feel real. The Sidemen have
OL,18,Fbeen such a huge part of my life for
OL,19,Fover 12-13 years.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU
