PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780326668
OL,3,C'Hardest video I've ever had to make':
OL,4,CKSI announces sudden Sidemen departure
OL,6,F"For almost half my life, this Sidemen
OL,7,Fhas been my second family. We've grown
OL,8,Fup together. We've travelled the world
OL,9,Ftogether.
OL,11,F"We built something that none of us
OL,12,Fever thought was possible especially
OL,13,Fback then when we were making random
OL,14,Fvideos together and playing GTA (Grand
OL,15,FTheft Auto)."
OL,17,FIn a statement posted on social media
OL,18,Fby Sidemen, the group said they were
OL,19,F"sad to share the news" about KSI's
OL,20,Fdeparture.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@MO]
