OL,3,C'Hardest video I've ever had to make':
OL,4,CKSI announces sudden Sidemen departure
OL,6,F"We had an amazing time on this
OL,7,Fjourney with him and we wish him all
OL,8,Fthe best with his future endeavours,"
OL,9,Fthey said.
OL,11,F"This came as a surprise to us and we
OL,12,Fknow it will be an adjustment for you,
OL,13,Fbut we've got lots of exciting stuff
OL,14,Fplanned that we can't wait to share."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
