OL,3,C'Hardest video I've ever had to make':
OL,4,CKSI announces sudden Sidemen departure
OL,6,FThe London-born star, who appeared in
OL,7,FSaturday's final of ITV's Britain's
OL,8,FGot Talent, said he remembered the
OL,9,Fgroup's early days on YouTube, and
OL,10,Fthat he had "no idea that tens of
OL,11,Fmillions of people were going to be
OL,12,Fwatching us on the channel".
OL,14,FHe said: "Together we've done things I
OL,15,Fnever thought were possible. We've
OL,16,Fsold out arenas, we sold out stadiums.
OL,17,FWe've broken records. We've made
OL,18,FNetflix shows, we've done a lot and
OL,19,Fwe've shared so many good moments on
OL,20,FYouTube and those moments will stay
OL,21,Fwith me for the rest of my life.
OL,26,@rD@MOUtD@[O]vD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
