OL,3,C'Hardest video I've ever had to make':
OL,4,CKSI announces sudden Sidemen departure
OL,6,F"We've been there for each other
OL,7,Fthrough some of the highest highs and
OL,8,Flowest lows of our lives. I've watched
OL,9,Fthese boys grow into incredible men.
OL,10,FI've watched them grow into fathers.
OL,11,FI've watched them grow into husbands.
OL,12,FAnd I'm so incredibly grateful to
OL,13,Fexperience that journey alongside them.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
