OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780326668
OL,3,C'Hardest video I've ever had to make':
OL,4,CKSI announces sudden Sidemen departure
OL,6,F"The truth is, nothing bad has
OL,7,Fhappened. This decision is completely
OL,8,Fmy own. Over the last few years, I've
OL,9,Ffelt myself being pulled in a lot of
OL,10,Fdirections than ever before. Between
OL,11,Feverything else in my life, I feel
OL,12,Flike I've been running at full speed,
OL,13,Fat 100mph."
OL,15,FHe said he had been "trying to be
OL,16,Feverything for everyone" and added he
OL,17,Fhad "started losing the balance in my
OL,18,Fown life" as a result, finding it
OL,19,F"hard to find time for my family".
