OL,3,C'Hardest video I've ever had to make':
OL,4,CKSI announces sudden Sidemen departure
OL,6,FKSI went on to thank each of the
OL,7,Fgroup's other members Simon Minter,
OL,8,FJosh Bradley, Vikram Barn, Tobi Brown,
OL,9,FEthan Payne, and Harry Lewis, and said
OL,10,Fthey "deserve somebody who can give
OL,11,F100%".
OL,13,FHe said: "I hope you'll continue
OL,14,Fsupporting the boys, because they
OL,15,Fdeserve it. They're still going to do
OL,16,Famazing things, I know they're still
OL,17,Fgoing to make incredible content, and
OL,18,FI'll definitely be watching alongside
OL,19,Fall of you.
OL,26,@rD@FOUsD@EO]uD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
