OL,3,C'Hardest video I've ever had to make':
OL,4,CKSI announces sudden Sidemen departure
OL,6,F"But for now, I need to focus on
OL,7,Fmyself, and I need to focus on fixing
OL,8,Fmy work-life balance, just so I can
OL,9,Ffinally focus on my health, and
OL,10,Ffinally make time to see my family and
OL,11,Fmake time to see my partner."
OL,13,FAlong with making YouTube videos, the
OL,14,Fgroup has launched its own fried
OL,15,Fchicken chain, clothing, alcohol, and
OL,16,Fcereal.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@]O]
